data.description: Welcome to this charming chalet-style located minutes from the heart of Clatskanie. This stunning property offers breathtaking views of the Clatskanie River and a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of city life. Easy access to major highways, near an hour to Portland, and 45 minutes to Vancouver.Home offers 2 bedrooms with a loft, warm hardwood floors, natural light, open kitchen, and a simple floor plan, with plenty of area to relax and unwind. Imagine sipping your morning coffee while gazing out at the grape orchard just beyond the deck or taking in the view from the comfort of your living room.    For those with electric vehicles, rejoice! This property comes equipped with an electric car plug-in, making it convenient to charge your vehicle right at home. Additionally, there is parking space available for up to six vehicles and an RV, ensuring ample room for everyone.Love the idea of sustainable living? You'll appreciate the chicken coop and raised garden on this property. Grow your own vegetables or enjoy farm-fresh eggs in the comfort of your own backyard.Step outside onto the large private deck and soak up the tranquil atmosphere. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or simply relaxing with a good book, this outdoor oasis provides the ideal setting.All kitchen appliance included in sale. Buyer to perform due dilgence to their satisfaction.
